  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "When it all becomes clear Your fears are here When it all becomes so crystal fucking clear It takes self-discipline To know when you're right To know when you're wrong You hear me or not It takes self-discipline To continue this fight Even though you've been wrong And you can't see anything From what you saw from before It takes self-discipline To ensure it's time to not Ignore all the cats at your doorstep Ignore all the ways That you can't take one more step Why is it that you brought yourself here again? It's just a fall It takes self-discipline To know that's not the end No, no, no It's just the beginning, my friend Of me And me seeing me Give a little self-discipline Make my dreams come true Send a kid ready to go You care about me, how will I do? It takes self-discipline to tell you all to go Fuckin' hell Bye-bye, motherfucker, bye-bye Hope you tell your story well Hope you tell how I was just so outrageous That I made you do shit I've been giving so fucking much And I just wanted a little accountability For the things you asked and how many times I saved you From the war inside of you But now I gotta love you So it's bye-bye Sorry if it needs something up in there But sorry, don't cut it no more You're just a fuckin' bore Would've given if you just would've asked But now I see that it's on me All these things I don't blame I forgive but don't worry We'll never get that close again I got self-discipline For me I don't need to hear Excuses of a mile long I know it's my choice to let me wrong So I build these walls up now So you never get past me That loves me, denies self-discipline I ain't buying nothing inside It's not the hype It's creating love unconditional for you Even though I'm the one that's fucked up now I know it's my choice if you'll let me in So I'm gonna give you a pass this time Motherfucker, this time There won't be a next time Believe that That self-discipline You can't see Your hate won't bring me down, motherfuckin' bitch",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 12.460000038146973,
      "text": "When it all becomes clear Your fears are here",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 20.600000381469727,
      "text": "When it all becomes so crystal fucking clear",
      "start": 12.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 25.719999313354492,
      "text": "It takes self-discipline To know when you're right",
      "start": 21.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 28.440000534057617,
      "text": "To know when you're wrong You hear me or not",
      "start": 25.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 32.540000915527344,
      "text": "It takes self-discipline To continue this fight",
      "start": 28.440000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 34.52000045776367,
      "text": "Even though you've been wrong",
      "start": 32.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 39.880001068115234,
      "text": "And you can't see anything From what you saw from before",
      "start": 35.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 45.58000183105469,
      "text": "It takes self-discipline To ensure it's time to not",
      "start": 39.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 49.70000076293945,
      "text": "Ignore all the cats at your doorstep Ignore all the ways",
      "start": 45.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 54.939998626708984,
      "text": "That you can't take one more step Why is it that you brought yourself here again?",
      "start": 49.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 57.84000015258789,
      "text": "It's just a fall",
      "start": 54.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 61.939998626708984,
      "text": "It takes self-discipline To know that's not the end",
      "start": 58.5
    },
    {
      "end": 64.22000122070312,
      "text": "No, no, no",
      "start": 62.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 65.9800033569336,
      "text": "It's just the beginning, my friend",
      "start": 64.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 68.86000061035156,
      "text": "Of me",
      "start": 67.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 73.76000213623047,
      "text": "And me seeing me",
      "start": 70.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 77.95999908447266,
      "text": "Give a little self-discipline Make my dreams come true",
      "start": 73.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 80.23999786376953,
      "text": "Send a kid ready to go",
      "start": 77.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 84.76000213623047,
      "text": "You care about me, how will I do?",
      "start": 80.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 88.22000122070312,
      "text": "It takes self-discipline to tell you all to go",
      "start": 85.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 91.4800033569336,
      "text": "Fuckin' hell",
      "start": 90.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 94.37999725341797,
      "text": "Bye-bye, motherfucker, bye-bye",
      "start": 91.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 96.77999877929688,
      "text": "Hope you tell your story well",
      "start": 94.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 99.23999786376953,
      "text": "Hope you tell how I was just so outrageous",
      "start": 96.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 102.4800033569336,
      "text": "That I made you do shit I've been giving so fucking much",
      "start": 99.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 105.77999877929688,
      "text": "And I just wanted a little accountability",
      "start": 102.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 110.41999816894531,
      "text": "For the things you asked and how many times I saved you",
      "start": 105.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 113.68000030517578,
      "text": "From the war inside of you",
      "start": 110.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 117.23999786376953,
      "text": "But now I gotta love you",
      "start": 113.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 120.0999984741211,
      "text": "So it's bye-bye",
      "start": 117.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 122.66000366210938,
      "text": "Sorry if it needs something up in there",
      "start": 120.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 124.5199966430664,
      "text": "But sorry, don't cut it no more",
      "start": 122.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 125.77999877929688,
      "text": "You're just a fuckin' bore",
      "start": 124.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 128.4600067138672,
      "text": "Would've given if you just would've asked",
      "start": 125.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 130.60000610351562,
      "text": "But now I see that it's on me",
      "start": 128.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 132.4600067138672,
      "text": "All these things I don't blame",
      "start": 130.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 134,
      "text": "I forgive but don't worry",
      "start": 132.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 136.60000610351562,
      "text": "We'll never get that close again",
      "start": 134
    },
    {
      "end": 138.52000427246094,
      "text": "I got self-discipline",
      "start": 136.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 143.4600067138672,
      "text": "For me",
      "start": 141.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 148.24000549316406,
      "text": "I don't need to hear",
      "start": 146
    },
    {
      "end": 150.97999572753906,
      "text": "Excuses of a mile long",
      "start": 148.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 153.97999572753906,
      "text": "I know it's my choice to let me wrong",
      "start": 150.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 157.60000610351562,
      "text": "So I build these walls up now",
      "start": 154.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 159.44000244140625,
      "text": "So you never get past me",
      "start": 157.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 162.44000244140625,
      "text": "That loves me, denies self-discipline",
      "start": 159.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 164.63999938964844,
      "text": "I ain't buying nothing inside",
      "start": 162.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 166.10000610351562,
      "text": "It's not the hype",
      "start": 164.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 169.63999938964844,
      "text": "It's creating love unconditional for you",
      "start": 167.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 171.94000244140625,
      "text": "Even though I'm the one that's fucked up now",
      "start": 169.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 174.44000244140625,
      "text": "I know it's my choice if you'll let me in",
      "start": 171.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 177.5399932861328,
      "text": "So I'm gonna give you a pass this time",
      "start": 175
    },
    {
      "end": 179.02000427246094,
      "text": "Motherfucker, this time",
      "start": 177.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 182.1999969482422,
      "text": "There won't be a next time",
      "start": 180.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 184.02000427246094,
      "text": "Believe that",
      "start": 182.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 186.4600067138672,
      "text": "That self-discipline",
      "start": 184.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 188.77999877929688,
      "text": "You can't see",
      "start": 187.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 194.6999969482422,
      "text": "Your hate won't bring me down, motherfuckin' bitch",
      "start": 191.36000061035156
    }
  ],
